{3000}{}{Name's Joseph. I am the miners' brigadier. Basically - my job here is to make sure the ore keeps flowing and miners are gettin' paid, that's all.}
{3010}{}{Why is ore so important?}
{3020}{}{Can I join mining works? What shall I do?}
{3030}{}{Let me ask you about something else...}
{4000}{}{Why? Lad, this town LIVES off ore mining. Mining ore and selling it is one of the main ways for the town to earn money. Without ore mining our local economy will most likely collapse.}
{4010}{}{Can I join mining works? What shall I do?}
{4020}{}{Let me ask you about something else...}
{5000}{}{Yeah, it is all easy in fact - find a party of miners and somebody with good guns to deal with parasites in the mines. The mines are located west from 'ere. Don't go there alone though. Once again - they are infested with parasites. Once ya collect some ore - use the furnace over here to smelt it. Once done - bring the results of ya work to me, I will pay ya with mining obligations. Ya can exchange em in RWU HQ for money or ya can buy some food from the "Charley" bot over there. [He waves towards the bot]}
{5010}{}{Why is ore so important?}
{5020}{}{Let me ask you about something else...}
{6000}{}{Do ya? Alright, I take NF_METAL bars and lead nuggets in quantaties of 10 only. Coal - in quantaties of 10. Minerals - in quantaties of 10. Iron bars - 10.}
