{8000}{}{Seriously? You know, I am kinda busy here, lad... Tell you what - if you really want to hear about my past then bring me a bottle of beer.}
{8010}{}{Fine, I will come later with your beer.}
{8020}{}{Here is your beer. Now... Mind telling your story?}
{9000}{}{Fine. [He takes a bottle of beer] What cna I say... My full name is Joseph Murray. I was born in Redding and wasted half of my youth being high as fuck on jet and trab the city was pumped with thanks to Mordino family. Then finally got my head together, got to known few very important people aaaaaaand... thanks to that managed to get into some really-really nice roles. Then was invited 'ere by Arthur Goldstein and used to help the loval administration to orginise the mining works... Till the revolt of course. Now I am here... still being a brigadier. I ain't complaining though - good positions, good money.}
